sequenceDiagram
  participant User as User
  participant Siri as HomePod Siri
  participant HA as Home Assistant
  participant A as Orchestrator
  participant P as Policy Gate
  participant L as JSONL Logger

  User->>Siri: "Hey Siri, Night Mode"
  Siri->>HA: Trigger Home Scene / Automation
  HA->>A: webhook/service call: night_mode request

  A->>P: evaluate(request, state, prefs)
  P-->>A: allow/deny + cooldown + safety_checks

  alt allowed
    A->>HA: call tools: dim light, set scene, optional AC adjust
    HA-->>A: tool responses (success + new state)
    A->>HA: verify state (light level / scene / climate)
    HA-->>A: verified/failed
  else denied
    A-->>HA: no-op (or safe alternative)
  end

  A->>L: write logs (cid, decisions, actions, latency)
  A->>HA: speak confirmation via TTS (HomePod)
